import React from 'react'
import { Card, Image, Container, Row, Col, Jumbotron } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'



function FeaturesCards ({ home }) {

    return (
        <>
        
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <Jumbotron>
                    {home.id === 3 || home.id === 2
                    ?
                        <Col sm={6}>
                            <Card>
                                <Image src={home.photos[2].image} fluid />
                            </Card>
                        </Col>
                        : null
                        }
                </Jumbotron>
            </Row>
        </Container>

        : null

}

export default FeaturesCards;
